${SMAY}>> Installation ${LSAMAY}Source RAMBO${SMAY} Completed ^_^ .\n
Now I Have Information For Your Bot  \n
1- Enter Token Your Bot .
2- Enter Your UserName Sudo .
3- And End Press Enter To Run Source Rambo .\n\n
